title: Survivorman - Off The Grid
description:
Survivorman - Les Stroud - Off The Grid

Video codec: XviD
Resolution: 512x384
Audio codec: mp3 160kbps
Duration: 1:07:24

In this poignant and personal documentary Les Stroud and Sue Jamison, along with their two young children, share their experience leaving a world of electricity bills and water problems and going &#039;off the grid&#039; as they move to their acreage in Northern Ontario - escaping the clutches of government controlled electricity and water.
